<title>USA: Wiztec Solutions Ltd Q1 net increases.</title>
<headline>Wiztec Solutions Ltd Q1 net increases.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Three months ended</p>
<p>					 March 31		Year ended</p>
<p>					    1997	 1996	 1996</p>
<p> REVENUES		     $   2,965,607  1,673,716  8,331,969</p>
<p> NET  INCOME			  577,028    524,874  1,613,480</p>
<p>EARNINGS  PER  SHARE</p>
<p> Net  income			     0.10	 0.12	 0.29</p>
<p>WEIGHTED  AVERAGE  NUMBER OF</p>
<p>   SHARES OUTSTANDING	   6,070,000  4,400,000  5,609,091</p>
<p>NOTE:  Earnings per share for the first quarter of 1997 reflects an increase in the average number of shares outstanding, from 4.4 million during the first quarter of 1996 to 6.1 million, as a result of the company's IPO in April 1996 and the acquisition of Business Systems Inc.</p>
